皇&nbsp;玉虚大帝&nbsp;虚无玉帝&nbsp;太微大帝&nbsp;少微大帝</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">天地始祖&nbsp;五老上帝恭望洪慈&nbsp;俯垂恩光</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">再运真香&nbsp;虔诚上启&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高上神霄九宸上帝</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">九天自然&nbsp;生神上帝&nbsp;十方太上&nbsp;灵宝天尊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">玉光境内&nbsp;宝盖会中&nbsp;天真大圣&nbsp;妙行真人</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">三清境界&nbsp;金阙玉京&nbsp;飞香芬馥&nbsp;开通六道</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">灵妃金仙&nbsp;玉女元君恭望洪慈&nbsp;俯垂恩光</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">再运真香&nbsp;虔诚上启&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">校经主宰天枢上相&nbsp;法主道德天尊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">南辰北斗&nbsp;大道星君&nbsp;上清十二&nbsp;大矅星君</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">天地水火&nbsp;四圣真君&nbsp;东西南北&nbsp;四法真君</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">骖随帝驾&nbsp;无鞅真圣&nbsp;三界官属&nbsp;十方真仙</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">冥阳列圣&nbsp;合座威灵&nbsp;城隍土地&nbsp;里域真官</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">神庙香火&nbsp;一切威灵&nbsp;悉仗真香&nbsp;普同供养</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文&nbsp;伏以&nbsp;太虚寥廓&nbsp;千真侍供于九重&nbsp;妙道混融</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">一气秘玄于八表&nbsp;日星月赫&nbsp;雨露无私</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">伏念臣等&nbsp;幸缘夙庆&nbsp;获际真风&nbsp;蓬心未达于玄关</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">蒿目难窥于圣域&nbsp;修奉行道&nbsp;惭无紫囊金简之文</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">酌水侍天&nbsp;赖有灵宝虚皇之教&nbsp;洁净庭宇</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">罗像世之威仪&nbsp;严值坛场&nbsp;备朝天之科范</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">竭一诚而拱北&nbsp;如万水以朝东&nbsp;谨炼鸳鹭之班</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">迎迓龙鸾之与&nbsp;圣驾既临于金殿&nbsp;衣冠齐拜</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">于紫宸&nbsp;望垂鉴佑之私&nbsp;少副精虔之祷</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">俱有迎鸾意文&nbsp;恭对敷宣</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">(追关)&nbsp;七元真气降&nbsp;八卦定君臣吾奉上帝敕&nbsp;有令急速来&nbsp;唵吽吽&nbsp;混元宗坛&nbsp;本坛都炉焚香&nbsp;下令宣召&nbsp;金阙门下&nbsp;传奏仙官&nbsp;功曹使者&nbsp;火速出班&nbsp;祈领关文&nbsp;通传表奏&nbsp;俱有护表关文&nbsp;谨当宣读</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">向伸关文&nbsp;宣白云周&nbsp;说于坛前&nbsp;用凭火化</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">志心皈命礼&nbsp;经坛土地&nbsp;云云</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">大赞&nbsp;&nbsp;清微宫&nbsp;显神通&nbsp;自然香遍满虚空</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">分身现化白玉京望金阙七宝装成</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">普放十七大光明鸾风唱啸歌咏咏</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">诸天诸地赞无穷愿众生瞻礼金容</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文&nbsp;伏以&nbsp;表文上达&nbsp;听聪灵音&nbsp;翘想云衢</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">对金阙而拜舞&nbsp;仰瞻帝座&nbsp;辞圣真以退班</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">俯伏恩光&nbsp;致恭三礼</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">提科&nbsp;一炷真香本自然&nbsp;黄庭炉内起祥烟</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;空中结说浮云篆&nbsp;上祝祖师寿万年</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">稽首皈依道&nbsp;道在杳冥中&nbsp;云云</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">提科&nbsp;金炉信香结珠烟&nbsp;祥光瑞气照大千</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">三岛神仙临法会十州诸真降人间</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">稽首皈依经&nbsp;经文焕八方&nbsp;云云</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">提科&nbsp;钟鼓琳琅响彻天&nbsp;十方萧净得安然</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天无氛秽朝元始&nbsp;地无妖尘谒帝颜</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">稽首皈依师&nbsp;师文焕八方&nbsp;云云</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">提科&nbsp;天开皇道五云祥&nbsp;仿佛瑶坛接帝乡</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;欲把丹诚通帝阙&nbsp;须凭道德一炉香</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文&nbsp;迎鸾以后&nbsp;罪灭福生&nbsp;恭对道前&nbsp;志心发愿</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">一愿乾坤明素&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;二愿气象清玄</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">三愿国土清平&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;四愿化洽八诞</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">五愿天垂甘露&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;六愿地发祥烟</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">七愿四时顺遂&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;八愿万物生全</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">九愿家多孝悌&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;十愿国富才贤</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">十一愿诸神拥护十二愿学道真诠</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">愿以此功德&nbsp;普及于一切&nbsp;迎鸾保平安&nbsp;消灾增福寿&nbsp;向来迎鸾接驾功德&nbsp;上奉高真&nbsp;下保平安</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">赐福消灾&nbsp;同赖善功证无上道&nbsp;一切信礼</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">志心称念&nbsp;玉皇赦罪天尊不可思议功德</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">接念&nbsp;高上玉皇心印妙经</span><br />', '1448432875', '1', '', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `fu_curlture` VALUES ('22', '扬 幡 科 仪', '<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：华幡高举扶长风，五色云中焕太空；</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;福国康民资圣泽，十方快都谢玄功。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">步虚：真文焕碧落，流景飞云芒；</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天光开黄道，灵霄礼虚皇。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">举天尊：总真应现天尊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">吊挂：华幡高举掛长杆，昭告百神第一端；</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;飞展东西如凤舞，飃颻上下似龙蟠。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;丹與绿辇来仙驾，羽盖琼轮降宝坛；</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;万圣千真临法会，证盟功德广无边。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">香供养：总真应现天尊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：伏以，降万道金光之气，丕阐灵通，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">命九风破秽之君，肃清尘界，静神风於宇宙，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">迎仙仗於瑶坛，列圣朝宗，诸天遥唱，上彰道化，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">下副凡情，谨炷真香，虔诚上啟。盖闻，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">尘居为浊界，秽气分葩，凡世异仙都，妖气混起，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">不凭激浊以扬清，安可迎真而驻驿。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">夫此水者，德冠五行，功资万物，为九天之雨露，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">作四海之波涛。圣人出而黄河清，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">王道平而泉涌源，今时一滴洒瑶坛，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">五浊六尘具洁净，水有灵章，谨当持诵。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">洒静：清静之水，日月华盖，中藏北斗，内隐三台。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">神水一洒，厌秽速开，净水洒过，祸去福来。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：吸呼浊，扬呼清，既使万魔束首，除其尘，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">荡其秽，自然六欲不生。一滴才沾，十方涓洁。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">举天尊：常清常静天尊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：维时天开黄道，胜兆元吉之庥，人举丹忱，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">炉烟达重霄之上，扬宝幡于空际，迓圣驭于云间，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">欲彩动龙驰，高悬金书之一丈，关虎豹，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">迎来玉府之群真，兹举告盟，必假香传。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">夫此香者，九阳回妙气，三景产元英，灵风舞炉烟，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">普现无边之圣，碧霭浮云篆，飞升好善之家，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">是谓祖本之天根，可迎仙圣而会集，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">爇向炉中，腾空供养。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">提纲：各礼师称念如法，请宣科奏。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">祝香咒：道由心学，………</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">威灵：玄坛肇啟，三界十方，金书玉字，凤篆龙章，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">咒&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;幡之为体，随风飘荡，光浮八极，丹凤翱翔，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">诸天会集，万幡开张，所指方面，共昭神贶，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">臣等皈命，与道合真。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">提纲：恭叩天颜，请称职位。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">称职：臣系太上，道德教下，清静正一，不二法门，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">南昌炼度，上宰北极，伏魔真人，便宜奉行，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">凡昧科事，臣***，&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;引领坛下，请法弟子，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">诚惶诚恐，稽首顿首。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">圣班：炉焚真香。虔诚上啟，虚无自然，至真三宝，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">玉清圣境，元始天尊，上清真境，灵宝天尊，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">太清仙境，道德天尊，恭望洪慈，洞垂照格。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">炉焚真香，虔诚上啟。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;太上开元执府，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">御历含真体道，昊天至尊，玉皇上帝，勾陈上宫，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">天皇大帝，中天星主，元皇上帝，承天效法，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">后土皇地祗，圣主圣后，二帝高真，高上神霄，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">洞真大梵，九辰上帝，十方至真自然，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">太上灵宝天尊，恭望洪慈，洞垂照格。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">炉焚真香，虔诚上啟。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天地始祖，五老上帝，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">大罗天皇，诸天上帝，天地人三皇道老，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">诸天宰辅，群阙高真，空境罗仙，碧霄真宰，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">周天列宿，河汉群真，三元三品，三官大帝，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">三宫九府，应感天尊，北极法主，四圣真君，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">天地水阳，四京上圣，玉堂省府，历代师真，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">九天天曹，三天圣众，上界云府高真，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">中界岳渎威灵，下界水乡仙哲，灵宝雷庭，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">诸司官将，太岁城隍，社令里域，功曹府使，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">传奏等神，监幡使者，黄道大神，虚空过往，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">一切真仙，悉仗真香，普同供养。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">（宣表文）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：伏以，斋心肇启，始潜乎里域之中，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">法篆谨肃，端叩于穹苍之上，谨以修崇之仪，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">用申启告之言，所具表文，上间圣造，宣化已白，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">按如嗣首，精诚恳切，瞻黄道以开天，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">布洪云而满地，一心皈命，五体投忱，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">惟冀九皇命驾，降凤辇于空中，万圣临轩，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">现龙车於众外，百神具至，三界济临。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">（无表从此按击尺朗白）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">举天尊：洪恩延布天尊</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：伏愿，高悬碧落，似丹凤以翱翔，真接清虚，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">如黄龙而幡舞，迎法驾以临轩，迓真灵而降驾，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">上通九九之天，金阙玄机，同盼旁周，六六之地，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">琳祠海岳尽知闻，群生开解悟之心，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">大道脱轮回之苦，大起因缘，同培善果，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">悬幡有偈，羽众同称。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">众唱：道场啟，法筵开，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;设斋悬幡扬五彩，一心叩仰紫金台，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;望天阙云路徘徊，三界十方济降鉴，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;随玉阶降福消灾，乘云驾鹤满空排，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;云霭霭帝驾临来，仙家乐，白鹤飞。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：伏以，圣造无私，不言善应，人心有祷，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">所愿皆从，向来扬立宝幡，飘迎圣驾，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">愿祈道力，印证良因，匪霞匪迩，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">告见善闻功德，克就拜谢洪恩，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">志心称念：招真集贤天尊，不可思议功德。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">（宣榜式）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：伏以，舒坛设像，严七宝之宫墙，挂榜悬幡，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">迎诸天而集会，下按于门，八卦土应于三界十方，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">遵琼笈之真科，演玉京之玄范，宏宣典格，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">乐奏均天，祗飚驭以来临，迎云辇而下迎，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">鉴观善事，照格凡情，所具迎真榜文，朗声宣读。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">（宣榜）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">向伸榜文，宣白云周，右请榜眼仙官，常加卫护，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">见闻真宰，辅合玄风，功成道备，名书上请。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">举天尊：圣智高悬天尊。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">说文：召告百神主者，祗迎海会群仙，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">盟真墨榜叫通天，期格圣贤，洞鉴享此，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">丹忱一举，佑我万善，同观惟祈，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">三宝证良缘，携登蟠桃大宴，</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">请众排班，引导回坛。</span><br />', '1448432934', '1', '', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `fu_curlture` VALUES ('23', '胎息经注', '<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">经名：胎息经注。题幻真先生注。一卷。底本出处：《正统道藏》洞真部玉诀类。参校版本：一、《道藏辑要》本，收入该书其集第九册。二、《道藏精华录》本，收入该书第七集。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">胎息经注</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">胎从伏气中结，</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">脐下三寸为气海，亦为下丹田，亦为玄牝。世人多以口鼻为玄牝，非也。口鼻即玄牝出入之门。盖玄者水也，牝者母也。世人以阴阳炁相感，结於水母，三月胎&nbsp;结，十月形体具而能生人。修道者，常伏其&nbsp;炁於脐下，守其神於身内，神炁相合而生玄胎，玄胎既结，乃自生身，即为内丹，不死之道也。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">气从有胎中息。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">神为炁子，炁为神母，神炁相逐，如形与影。胎母既结，即神子自息，即元炁不散。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">气入身来为之生，神去离形为之死。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">《西升经》云：身者神之舍，神者身之主也。主人安静，神即居之；主人躁动，神即去之。神去无散，安可得生？是以人耳目手足，皆不能自运，叉假神以御之。学道养生之人，常拘其神以为神主，主既不去，宅岂崩坏也。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">知神气可以长生，固守虚无以养神气。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">道经云：我命在我，不在天地。天地所息人不能知至道，能知而不能行。知者但能虚心绝虑，保炁养精，不为外境爱欲所牵，恬淡以养神炁，即长生之道毕矣。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">神行即&nbsp;炁行，神住即炁住。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">所谓意是无马，行止相随，欲使元炁不离玄牝，即先拘守至神，神不离身，无亦不散，自然内实，不饥不渴也。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">若欲长生，神气相注。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">相注者，即是神炁不相离。《玄纲》云：锱铢阴炁不灭不为鬼，纤毫阴炁不尽不为仙。元炁即阳炁也，食炁即阴炁也，常喊食节欲，使元炁内运，元炁若壮，即阴&nbsp;炁自消；阳壮阴衰则百病不作，神安体悦，可觊长生矣。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">心不动念，无来无去，不出不入，自然常住。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">神之与炁，在母腹中本是一体之物，及生下为外境爱欲所牵，未尝一息暂归於本。人知此道，常泯绝情念，勿使神之出入去来，能不忘，久而习之，神自住矣。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">勤而行之，是真道路。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">修真之道，备尽於斯。然圣人之言，不可妄乎！几胎息用功后，关节开通，毛发疏畅，即但鼻中微微引炁，相从四支百毛孔中出，往而不返也。后炁续到，但引之而不吐也。切切於徐徐，虽云引而不吐，所引亦不入於喉中，微微而散。如此，内&nbsp;炁亦下流散矣。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">胎息铭</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">三十六咽，一咽为先。吐唯细细，纳唯绵绵。坐外亦尔，行立坦然。戒於喧杂，忌以腥膻。假名胎息，实日内丹。非只治病，央定延年。久久行之，名列上仙。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">胎息经注竟</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<br />', '1448433063', '0', '', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `fu_curlture` VALUES ('24', '《太上感应篇》', '<p style=\"font-family:宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">太上曰：祸福无门，唯人自召。善恶之报，如影随形。是以天地有司过之神依人犯轻重，以夺人算。算减则贫耗，多逢忧患，人皆恶之，刑祸随之，吉庆避之，恶星灾之，算尽则死。又有三台北斗神君，在人头上，录人罪恶，夺其纪算。又有三尸神，在人身中，每到庚申日，辄上诣天曹，言人罪过。月晦之日，灶神亦然。凡人有过，大则夺纪，小则夺算。其过大小，有数百事，欲求长生者，先须避之。是道则进，非道则退。不履邪径，不欺暗室。积德累功，慈心於物。忠孝友悌，正己化人，矜孤恤寡，犹老怀幼。昆虫草木，犹不可伤。宜悯人之凶，乐人之善，济人之急，救人之危。见人之得，如己之得。见人之失，如己之失。不彰人短，不炫己长。遏恶扬善，推多取少。受辱不怨，受宠若惊。施恩不求报，与人不追悔。所谓善人，人皆敬之天道佑之，福禄随之。众邪远之，神灵卫之，所作必成，神仙可冀。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">欲求天仙者，当立一千三百善，欲求地仙者，当立三百善苟或非义而动，背理而行。以恶为能，忍作残害。阴贼良善，暗侮君亲。慢其先生，叛其所事。诳诸无识，谤诸同学。虚诬诈为，攻讦宗亲。刚强不仁，狠戾自用。是非不当，向背乖宜。虐下取功，谄上希旨。受恩不感，念怨不休。轻蔑天民，扰乱国政。赏及非义，刑及无辜。杀人取财，倾人取位。诛降戮服，贬正排贤。凌孤逼寡，弃法受贿。以直为曲，以曲为直。入轻为重，见杀加怒。知过不改，知善不为。自罪引他，壅塞方术。讪谤贤圣，侵凌道德。射飞逐走，发蛰惊栖，填穴覆巢，伤胎破卵。愿人有失，毁人成功。危人自安，减人自益。以恶易好，以私废公。窃人之能，蔽人之善。形人之丑，讦人之私。耗人货财，离人骨肉。侵人所爱，助人为非，逞志作威，辱人求胜。败人苗稼，破人婚姻。苟富而骄，苟免无耻，认恩推过。嫁祸卖恶。沽买虚誉，包贮险心。挫人所长，扬己所短。乘威迫胁，纵暴杀伤。无故剪裁，非礼烹宰。散弃五谷，劳扰众生。破人之家。取其财宝。决水放火，以害民居，紊人规模，以败人功，损人器物，以穷人用。见他荣贵，愿他流贬。见他富有，愿他破散。见他色美，起心科之。负他货财，原他身死。干求不遂，便生咒恨。见他失便，便说他过。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">见他体相不具而笑之。见他才能可称而抑之。埋蛊厌人，用药杀树。恚怒师傅，抵触父兄。强取强求，好侵好夺。掳掠致富，巧诈求迁。赏罚不平，逸乐过节。苛虐其下，恐吓於他。怨天尤人，呵风骂雨。斗合争讼，妄逐朋党。用妻妾语，违父母训。得新忘故。口是心非，贪冒於财，欺罔其上。造作恶语，谗毁平人。毁人称直，骂神称正，弃顺效逆，背亲向疏。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">指天地以证鄙坏，引神明而监猥事。施与後悔，假借不还。分外营求，力上施设。淫欲过度，心毒貌慈。秽食馁人，左道惑众。短尺狭度，轻秤小升。以伪杂真，采取奸利。压良为贱，谩蓦愚人，贪婪无厌，咒诅求直。嗜酒悖乱，骨肉忿争。男不忠良，女不柔顺。不和其室，不敬其夫。每好矜夸，常行妒忌。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">无行於妻子，失礼於舅姑，轻慢先灵，违逆上命。作为无益，怀挟外心。自咒咒他，偏憎偏爱。越井越灶，跳食跳人。损子堕胎，行多隐僻。晦腊歌舞，朔旦号怒。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">对北涕唾及溺，对灶吟咏及哭。又以灶火烧香，秽柴作食。夜起露，八节行刑。唾流星，指虹霓。指三光，久视日月，春月燎腊，对北恶骂。无故杀龟打蛇，如是等罪，司命随其轻重，夺其纪算。算尽则死，死有余责，乃殃及子孙。又诸横取人财者，乃计其妻子家口以当之，渐至死丧。若不死丧，则有水火盗贼，遗亡器物，疾病口舌诸事，以当妄取之直。又枉杀人者，是易刀兵而相杀也。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:20px;line-height:normal;\">取非羲之财者，譬如漏脯救饥，鸩酒止渴，非不暂饱，死亦及之。夫心起於善，善虽未为，而吉神已随之。或心起於恶，恶虽未为，而凶神已随之。其有曾行恶事，後自改悔，诸恶莫作，众善奉行。久久必获吉庆，所谓转祸为福也。故吉人语善，视善，行善。一日有三善，三年天必降之福。凶人语恶、视恶、行恶，一日有三恶，三年天必降之祸，胡不勉而行之。</span>\r\n</p>', '1448433102', '0', '', '', '', '');
